"hail" or "hallelujah."

00:56:17.685 --> 00:56:23.002
And "Bhagavan" is the
living presence within us,

00:56:23.002 --> 00:56:26.260
the love that lives within us.

00:56:26.260 --> 00:56:29.244
It's who we truly are.

00:56:29.244 --> 00:56:37.446
When we sing Jay Bhagavan, we
sing victory to our own hearts.

00:56:37.446 --> 00:56:41.438
May that love conquer
all the darkness.

