good way, with an open heart,

01:00:48.690 --> 01:00:54.640
and without fear, it's only
because of the great beings

01:00:54.640 --> 01:00:58.329
that have gone before us.

01:00:58.329 --> 01:01:02.802
And out of their love,
out of their kindness,

01:01:02.802 --> 01:01:08.766
they left some footprints
for us to follow.

01:01:08.766 --> 01:01:15.812
So In the same way
that they wish for us,

01:01:15.812 --> 01:01:21.150
we wish that all beings
everywhere, all of us,

01:01:21.150 --> 01:01:26.270
be safe, be happy,
that all of us

01:01:26.270 --> 01:01:30.010
have good health
and enough to eat.

01:01:30.010 --> 01:01:34.460
And may we all live
in peace and at

01:01:34.460 --> 01:01:41.236
ease of heart, at ease
of heart, with whatever

01:01:41.236 --> 01:01:42.730
